sentence.text: This result has clinical and genetic counseling implications for genetically unsolved male case subjects with a classic motile cilium assembly phenotype that lack additional phenotypes such as intellectual disability or retinitis pignegative regulation of phosphatase activitytosa
Defects in motile cilia and sperm flagella cause primary ciliary dyskinesia (motile cilium assembly), characterized by chronic airway disease, infertility, and left-right body axis disturbance.
